quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Jab aasman phatt jayega
  84,2,Aur apne Rubb kay famaan ki tameel karega aur uske liye haq yahi hai (ke apne Rubb ka hukum maney)
  84,3,Aur jab zameen phaila di jayegi
  84,4,Aur jo kuch uske andar hai usey bahar phenk kar khaali ho jayegi
  84,5,Aur apne Rubb ke hukum ki tameel karegi aur uske liye haq yahi hai (kay uski tameel karey)
  84,6,Aey insaan tu kashaan kashaan apne Rubb ki taraf chala ja raha hai(striving unto your Lord) aur ussey milney wala hai
  84,7,Phir jiska naam-e-aamal uske seedhey haath mei diya gaya
  84,8,Ussey halka hisaab liya jayega
  84,9,Aur woh apne logon ki taraf khush khush paltega
  84,10,Raha woh shaks jiska naam-e-aamal us ki peeth ke pichey diya jayega
  84,11,To woh maut ko pukarega
  84,12,Aur bhadakti hui aag mei ja padega
  84,13,Woh apne ghar walon mein magan tha
  84,14,Usne samjha tha ke usey kabhi palatna nahin hai
  84,15,"Palatna kaise na tha, uska Rubb uske kartoot dekh raha tha"
  84,16,Pas nahin mai kasam khata hon shafaq(twilight) ki
  84,17,Aur raat ki aur jo kuch woh sameith leti hai
  84,18,Aur chaand ki jabke woh maah-e-kaamil (full) ho jata hai
  84,19,Tumko zaroor darja ba darja ek haalat se dusri halat ki taraf guzarte chalay jana hai
  84,20,Phir in logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh imaan nahin laatey
  84,21,Aur jab Quran inke samney pada jata hai to sajda nahin karte
  84,22,Balke yeh munkireen to ulta jhutlatay hain
  84,23,Halaanke jo kuch yeh (apne naam-e-aamal mein) jama kar rahey hain Allah usey khoob janta hai
  84,24,Lihaza inko dardnaak azaab ki basharat dedo
  84,25,Albatta jo log imaan le aaye hain aur jinho ne neik aamal kiye hain unke liye kabhi khatam na honay wala ajar hai
  85,1,Kasam hai mazboot qalon waley (impregnable castles )aasman ki
  85,2,Aur us din ki jiska wada kiya gaya hai
  85,3,Aur dekhnay walay ki aur dekhi janey wali cheez ki
  85,4,kay maarey gaye gaddey(pit) waley
  85,5,"uss gaddey(pit) waley] jis mei khoob bhadakte huey indhan ki aag thi"
  85,6,jabke woh us gaddey ke kinare par baithay huey thay
  85,7,Aur jo kuch woh imaan laney walon ke saath kar rahey thay usey dekh rahey thay
  85,8,Aur un ehley imaan se unki dushmani iske siwa kisi wajah se na thi ke woh us khuda par imaan le aaye thay jo zabardast aur apni zaat mei aap mahmood(praiseworthy) hai
  85,9,"Jo aasmano aur zameen ki sultanat ka maalik hai, aur woh khuda sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  85,10,"Jin logon ne momin mardon aur auraton par zulm o sitam toda aur phir ussey taib na huey, yaqeenan unke liye jahannum ka azaab hai aur unke liye jalaye janey ki saza hai"
  85,11,"Jo log imaan laaye aur jinho ne neik amal kiye yaqeenan unke liye jannat ke baagh hain jinke nichey nehrein behti hongi, yeh hai badi kamyabi"
  85,12,Dar haqeeqat tumharey Rubb ki pakad badi sakht hai
  85,13,Wahi pehli baar paida karta hai aur wahi dobara paida karega
  85,14,"Aur woh bakshne wala hai, mohabbat karne wala hai"
  85,15,"Arsh ka maalik hai, buzurg-o-bartar hai"
  85,16,Aur jo kuch chahey kar daalney wala hai
  85,17,Kya tumhey lashkaron ki khabar pahunchi hai
  85,18,Firoun aur samood (ke lashkaron) ki
  85,19,Magar jinho ne kufr kiya hai woh jhutlaney mein lagey huey hain
  85,20,Halaanke Allah ne unko gherey mein le rakha hai
  85,21,(unke jhutlaney se iss quran ka kuch nahin bigadta) balkey yeh quran buland paya hai
  85,22,Us loah mei (naqsh hai) jo mehfooz hai
  86,1,Kasam hai aasmaan ki aur raat ko namudaar honay wale ki
  86,2,Aur tum kya jaano kay woh raat ko namudaar honay wala kya hai
  86,3,Chamakta hua tara
  86,4,koi jaan aisi nahin hai jiske upar koi nigehbaan na ho
  86,5,Phir zara Insan yahi dekh le ke woh kis cheez se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,6,Ek uchalne wale pani se paida kiya gaya hai
  86,7,Jo peet aur seeney ki haddiyon kay darmiyan se nikalta hai
  86,8,Yaqeenan woh (khaliq) usey dobara paida karne par qadir hai
  86,9,Jis roz poshida asraar ki jaanch padtal hogi
  86,10,Us waqt Insan ke paas na khud apna koi zoar hoga aur na koi uski madad karne wala hoga
  86,11,Kasam hai baarish barsane waley aasman ki
  86,12,Aur (nabataat ugte waqt) phatt jane wali zameen ki
  86,13,Yeh ek jachi-tuli baat hai
  86,14,Hasi mazak nahin hai
  86,15,yeh log kuch chalein chal rahe hain
  86,16,Aur mai bhi ek chaal chal raha hoon
  86,17,"Pas chodh do aey nabi, in kafiron ko ek zara ki zara in ke haal par chod do"